Extract the DependencyManager from an InsertUpdate

Source: R/aaa-generics.R
dm.Rd

Retrieves the updated dependency_manager stored inside an insert_update object, allowing continued use after an insert() call.

Usage

dm(update)

Arguments

update

An insert_update object.

Value

A dependency_manager object.

See also

insert(), is_empty()
